title: Mikrotik RouterOS 3.22 x86
description:
1. install routeros 3.22 on hard disk
2. burn the routeros-key.iso and boot from it
3. login 'root' with no password
4. type:  roskey /dev/hda KEY-YOU-WANT
   LF15-2JT & VY3P-XNN is L5 with superchannel,
   Wait, it can take a while depending on your processor and HD size.
5. boot routeros
6. use selected keyfile in winbox or terminal to unblock routeros.

or

1. install 3.20 on hd
2. install keygen-3.20.npk
3. ssh to box.
!!! use ssh.exe from <a href=" http://blogimg.chinaunix.net/blog/upfile2/090313093752.rar" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://blogimg.chinaunix.net/blog/upfile2/090313093752.rar</a> !!
4. type roskey /dev/hda KEY-YOU-WANT
5. unblock with file
6. upgrade to 3.22 




works up to 3.22
